    "content": "1. 코시-오일러 제차미분방정식 형태1 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026x^2y''+axy'+by=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026D^2+\\left(a-1\\right)D+b=0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ 형태2 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026xy^{\\prime}+ay=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026D+a=0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ 2. 서로 다른, 실수 해 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha,\\beta \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^{\\alpha}+c_2x^{\\beta}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$x^2y''-4xy'+6y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D-3\\right)\\left(D-2\\right)=0\\rightarrow D=3,2 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^3+c_2x^2\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$x^2y''-xy'-y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2-2D-1=0\\rightarrow D=1\\pm\\sqrt{2} \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^{1+\\sqrt{2}}+c_2x^{1-\\sqrt{2}}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample3)\n$$xy''-y'=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D\\left(D-2\\right)=0\\rightarrow D=2,0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^2+c_2\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample4)\n$$x^3y''+2x^2y'-6xy=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D+3\\right)\\left(D-2\\right)=0 \\rightarrow D=-3,2 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1e^{-3x}+c_2e^{2x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r2. 중근 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=\\left(c_1+c_2\\ln x\\right)x^{\\alpha}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$xy''+y'=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2=0 \\rightarrow D=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1+c_2\\ln x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$x^2y''-xy'+y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D-1\\right)^2=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=\\left(c_1+c_2\\ln x\\right)x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r3. 서로 다른, 복소수 해 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha\\pm i\\beta \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=x^{\\alpha}\\left(c_1\\cos\\beta\\ln x+c_2\\sin\\beta\\ln x\\right) \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^{\\alpha+i\\beta}+c_2x^{\\alpha-i\\beta}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$x^2y''+xy'+y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2+1=0\\rightarrow D=\\pm i \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1\\cos\\left(\\ln x\\right)+c_2\\sin\\left(\\ln x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$x^2y''+3xy'+3y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2+2D+3=0\\rightarrow D=-1\\pm i\\sqrt{2} \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=x^{-1}\\left(c_1\\cos\\sqrt{2}\\ln x+c_2\\sin\\sqrt{2}\\ln x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$",
    "description": "1. 코시-오일러 제차미분방정식 형태1 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026x^2y''+axy'+by=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026D^2+\\left(a-1\\right)D+b=0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ 형태2 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026xy^{\\prime}+ay=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026D+a=0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ 2. 서로 다른, 실수 해 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha,\\beta \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^{\\alpha}+c_2x^{\\beta}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$x^2y''-4xy'+6y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D-3\\right)\\left(D-2\\right)=0\\rightarrow D=3,2 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^3+c_2x^2\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$x^2y''-xy'-y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2-2D-1=0\\rightarrow D=1\\pm\\sqrt{2} \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1x^{1+\\sqrt{2}}+c_2x^{1-\\sqrt{2}}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample3)",
